1) Write a CUDA program to read a sentence with equal length words. Count the no. of times a given word is repeated in the sentence. Use Atomic functions.

Sample string: Pcap EEFM exam Pcap test Pcap
Word: Pcap
Given word repeated 3 times 

2)Write a CUDA program to multiply 2 matrixes for the following specification:
	a) Each row resultant matrix to be computed by 1 thread
	b) Each column resultant matrix to be computed by 1 thread
	c) Each element of resultant matrix to be computed by 1 thread
	d) Using 2D Grid and 2D Block